measurements.description:
One large flower on one 14-cm staked inflorescence; dorsal sepal recurved, 
	downy, white, veined purple, distal strong reticulations purple; synsepal white, 
	veined purple; petals down-swept, recurved, white, veined purple, overlaid green proximally, 
	superior margins edged purple, hirsute, margins undulate; pouch pale chartreuse, 
	veined light mahogany, darker mahogany vein centrally, heavily speckled purple internally; 
	staminode chartreuse, stippled purple, superior half reticulated green; substance firm; 
	texture velvet, pouch glossy.
